@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rkhbba(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(tmp) + (0.94 - (tmp + 0.54 - v1 + 0.69)))
    tmp = (0.03 - (wp.cos(v0 + 0.81) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.22)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(v2) / tmp)
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.45 / v2 + 0.02) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.86)))
    v1 = (v1 - wp.exp((v1 + 0.84 * tmp + 0.18)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
